; Fixture journal for /api/flow regression: accounts with non-zero opening
; balance but zero movement in the queried month must still surface.
;
; Setup for month=2026-04:
;   - liabilities:cartão:bb-visa   → outstanding fatura from March, NO April
;     activity. Must appear with saldo_inicial != 0, all movement zero, and
;     saldo_final == saldo_inicial.
;   - liabilities:cartão:nubank    → has April activity. Sanity check that
;     the existing "active" path still works.
;   - assets:bank                  → has activity (pays the Nubank fatura
;     and receives salary). Sanity check.
;   - assets:savings               → opened with 1000 in January, NEVER
;     touched again. Must still appear in April with saldo 1000 and zero
;     movement.

account assets:bank
account assets:savings
account income:salary
account expenses:groceries
account liabilities:cartão:bb-visa
account liabilities:cartão:nubank

2026-01-01 * Opening
    assets:bank                          5000.00
    assets:savings                       1000.00
    equity:opening

; ── March: spend on BB Visa, leave fatura unpaid into April.
2026-03-10 * Mercado on BB
    expenses:groceries                    400.00
    liabilities:cartão:bb-visa

; ── March: salary so the user has something to spend with.
2026-03-25 * Salary
    assets:bank                          3000.00
    income:salary

; ── April: only Nubank activity, plus a transfer/payment from bank.
;     BB Visa is intentionally untouched.
2026-04-05 * Supermarket on Nubank
    expenses:groceries                    200.00
    liabilities:cartão:nubank

2026-04-20 * Pagamento Nubank
    assets:bank                          -100.00
    liabilities:cartão:nubank
